Overview

This project is built using R and RStudio. This software is open-source and provides a set of statistical tools that can collect, curate and generate reproducible reports for business and research. In this small demo project I have used these tools to access and visualise the data associated with fridge temperatures manually recorded in a google form and stored as a google sheet. This dashboard updates the .csv file in the data folder from the google forms data through google sheets API. The overall project structure is as follows:
